article.description: — Aaron Deloney scored 18 points as Vermont defeated Colgate 78-68 on Wednesday.
article.headline: Deloney carries Vermont past Colgate 78-68
article.story: BURLINGTON, Vt. -- — Aaron Deloney scored 18 points as Vermont defeated Colgate 78-68 on Wednesday. Ryan Davis and Isaiah Powell added 17 points each for Vermont (8-4), which earned its fourth straight home victory. Tucker Richardson scored a season-high 21 points and had six rebounds for the Raiders (4-9), who have now lost four straight games. Jack Ferguson added 16 points and nine rebounds. Keegan Records had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
